                        Loading your resume database...<br><br>
                        You can ask me questions like:<br>
                        • "Who has Python skills?"<br>
                        • "Find candidates with 5+ years experience"<br>
                        • "Show me hardware engineers"<br>
                        • "Who graduated from top universities?"
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="typing-indicator" id="typingIndicator">
                    <span></span>
                    <span></span>
                    <span></span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="chat-input-container">
                <div class="quick-questions" id="quickQuestions" style="display: none;">
                    <div class="quick-question" onclick="askQuestion('Who has the most experience?')">
                        Most experienced?
                    </div>
                    <div class="quick-question" onclick="askQuestion('Show candidates with Python skills')">
                        Python skills?
                    </div>
